   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>"Year 9 of Marcus Aurelius Severus Alexander Pius Felix Augustus, Epeiph 30. Maximos, son of N. N., his mother being Demetria, a private person, through Julia Alypia, has paid for bath-tax of the 9th year for Theadelphia one hundred dr(achmas), total 100 dr(achmas)."</ab>
